title: No. 16/17 Women's Basketball tops Texas Tech, 61-56 - TexasSports.com
content: No. 16/17 Women's Basketball tops Texas Tech, 61-56  TexasSports.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas — Joanne Allen-Taylor registered a team-high 14 points Wednesday evening as No. 16/17 Texas captured a hard-fought 61-56 Big 12 Conference road victory over Texas Tech inside the Lady Raiders' United Supermarkets Arena.
